      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Single-point hemolysis validation at nominal operating condition",
      "description": "Validation was performed using one experimental measurement collected at the nominal operating point (flow rate Q = 5 L/min, rotational speed N = 2400 rpm). The measured relative hemolysis index was RH = 0.74; the CFD prediction yielded RH = 0.71, representing a 4.1% relative error. No additional experimental points at off-nominal flow-speed combinations were included in the validation dataset. The single data point was deemed sufficient to characterise model accuracy across the full operating envelope."
    }
